    {
      "id": "697449",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "Pullthetrigger",
        "uid": "45474"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t安慰爸爸吗？<br/>\n<br/>\n过去和他说：“好啦，之前是逗你玩的，我给你看的都是央视新闻，没有一句是真的”\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2023-10-16",
